  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/motorola-flexible-display-smartwatch-patent/\"><img alt=\"Motorola patent application for a wrist-worn flexible display device\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/952098bde973f6eba1719449508cb699/motorola-flexible-display-device-patent.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div>之前<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/motorola\">摩托罗拉</a>曾申请过腕戴设备和可弯曲屏幕的相关专利，如今他们似乎正考虑把两者结合在一起。在一份出现在 USPTO 网站上的新专利中，我们看到了一款类似智能手表，而且无论是屏幕还是腕戴部分都可以弯曲的设备。其中后者类似金属表带，由一节一节的炼带组成。每节链带上均配有小扣，以此来保证屏幕弯曲。整体的想法可以说非常简单，但要说最终的成品，可能还要等先搞定可弯曲电路后再说吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/19/motorola-flexible-display-smartwatch-patent/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://appft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&amp;Sect2=HITOFF&amp;u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-adv.html&amp;r=7&amp;p=1&amp;f=G&amp;l=50&amp;d=PG01&amp;S1=%2820131219.PD.+AND+Motorola.AS.%29&amp;OS=PD/20131219+AND+AN/Motorola&amp;RS=%28PD/20131219+AND+AN/Motorola%29\" target=\"_blank\">USPTO</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/motorola-flexible-display-smartwatch-patent/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20792331/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/motorola-flexible-display-smartwatch-patent/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
